  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ZndY4bCV\">我推荐 <b>Anki</b></p><p data-pid=\"2wACV3h9\">Anki 是一个能够<b>记笔记</b>、以<b>自测</b>的形式复习、有复习安排<b>算法</b>的软件。</p><p data-pid=\"jwUTn9hZ\">用 Anki 复习笔记是这样的：</p><p data-pid=\"qoAE7_NK\">英语：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd21f281c773417770ceea3d08fb7cbe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-7aff51b7b3183166b582ebcd3e97048a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-192326b8463b4328472845fe78c823c3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dd21f281c773417770ceea3d08fb7cbe_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1081&#39; height=&#39;960&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-7aff51b7b3183166b582ebcd3e97048a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-192326b8463b4328472845fe78c823c3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dd21f281c773417770ceea3d08fb7cbe_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dd21f281c773417770ceea3d08fb7cbe_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>左边是正面问题，右边是背面答案</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"3Wo3LXxP\">生物：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dbcd67da83122a7178fb0f1d2cae9a77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-06d34c250f415f90699f6df834d717b7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7593ec449d9c091b6ece07673ebb9cf2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dbcd67da83122a7178fb0f1d2cae9a77_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1081&#39; height=&#39;960&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-06d34c250f415f90699f6df834d717b7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7593ec449d9c091b6ece07673ebb9cf2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-dbcd67da83122a7178fb0f1d2cae9a77_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-dbcd67da83122a7178fb0f1d2cae9a77_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"CZN7GBpe\">化学：<br/></p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-48541310be5afa9e24f2b6c4ae157944_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-21e4bf3d8f30be2013c397a11d6f8761\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cdd32379e563b6d2bafbe95ddc423c2a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-48541310be5afa9e24f2b6c4ae157944_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1081&#39; height=&#39;960&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1081\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-21e4bf3d8f30be2013c397a11d6f8761\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cdd32379e563b6d2bafbe95ddc423c2a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1081\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-48541310be5afa9e24f2b6c4ae157944_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-48541310be5afa9e24f2b6c4ae157944_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"mTi0UA9m\">Anki 会详细记录每次复习（自测）的情况：</p><figure data-size=\"small\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1714128aa3114bfb8e40e7983f24f75_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-4656fb6641ab088b865ff9d4f09f1d8e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f0b47e1c3a16ed0d7333ca705386b86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c1714128aa3114bfb8e40e7983f24f75_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1080&#39; height=&#39;2280&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"small\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2280\" data-original-token=\"v2-4656fb6641ab088b865ff9d4f09f1d8e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-3f0b47e1c3a16ed0d7333ca705386b86_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c1714128aa3114bfb8e40e7983f24f75_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c1714128aa3114bfb8e40e7983f24f75_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"GQyrpNxt\">我高二到高三用 Anki 记了超多笔记：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f51b4f7a58be466e408e711fa3ae7ca_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-f28783859e92a8d441904f255b792903\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6d2a398d3d7431d948845a552b105c41_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2f51b4f7a58be466e408e711fa3ae7ca_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;540&#39; height=&#39;960&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"540\" data-rawheight=\"960\" data-original-token=\"v2-f28783859e92a8d441904f255b792903\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-6d2a398d3d7431d948845a552b105c41_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"540\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2f51b4f7a58be466e408e711fa3ae7ca_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2f51b4f7a58be466e408e711fa3ae7ca_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"SyLuU43c\"><b>还没高三</b>的同学可以上手试试（高三的同学还是别刷知乎了）</p><p data-pid=\"v372aJKE\">下面是我高考前的统计数据：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1665&#39; height=&#39;3420&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1665\" data-rawheight=\"3420\" data-original-token=\"v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1665\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9df4555ff3ff0743ee50d92c09b51c0a_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/><figcaption>这个是电脑端的统计数据</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"sw3bxZbV\">Anki 相关的认知科学理论：</p><ul><li data-pid=\"RV9bAhSa\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57020308\" class=\"internal\">间隔重复</a></li><li data-pid=\"_R-jfxrb\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57113246\" class=\"internal\">测试效应</a></li><li data-pid=\"cmjqu-s_\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57139724\" class=\"internal\">穿插练习</a></li></ul><hr/><p data-pid=\"faqNwD2y\">Anki 支持 windows、mac、linux、安卓、苹果等常见设备，并且可以多端同步，走到哪学到哪。</p><p data-pid=\"2oe1rMSy\">为了帮到有缘人，我写了一份快速上手教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/61564332\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2e8a109841199b0a18e70ae7bd16ea66_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1220\" data-image-height=\"535\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：B 站 Ankidroid 视频教程与电子书(全平台教程)快速通道</a>",
